com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data

Class URLActionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data.URLActionData

  • public class URLActionData
extends java.lang.Object

    Data Container which holds all necessary information to create and validate a single http request.

    • Supports automatic & dynamic parameter interpretation via ParameterInterpreter.
    • Attributes are of type String to allow parameter interpretation and may be parsed to the intended type when they are accessed.
    • Defaults common used Http request values, if not set explicitly.
    • Holds a list of response validations.
    • Holds a list of variables which should be taken out of the response for dynamic parameter interpretation.
    Author:
    Matthias Mitterreiter
